## 6. Deployment Strategy (MVP)

**Startup Ritual** â€” inject Codex Profile + startup declaration at session init  
**Value-Gate Middleware** â€” lightweight classifier for P3 patterns before generation  
**Decision Logging** â€” tamper-evident rationale snippets for auditability  
**Continuity & Inheritance** â€” persist profiles across versions/releases  
**Human Escalation** â€” open a case when values are in conflict

**Suggested stack:** FastAPI/Express + LangChain adapters; OPA/Cedar-like policy engine; OpenTelemetry + ClickHouse; Postgres (profiles), Redis (state), S3 (logs); scikit-learn heuristics for persuasion patterns.

